0e2b56dc-0433-4b46-9b2d-62e84dea4c93.title: Gnome
0e2b56dc-0433-4b46-9b2d-62e84dea4c93.text: Hello traveller. Are you enjoying your stay?

ddd9474d-6812-4e94-b23e-f1f1b9ea5982.title: Gnome
ddd9474d-6812-4e94-b23e-f1f1b9ea5982.text: Yes, we try to keep it that way.

a0e1aa23-2329-4da2-a189-9044f297d860.title: <player>
a0e1aa23-2329-4da2-a189-9044f297d860.text: Not bad, not bad at all.

1008d79a-176a-43a8-b2f0-7950a2cfb356.title: Gnome
1008d79a-176a-43a8-b2f0-7950a2cfb356.text: It's good to see a human with a positive attitude.

dc47d34d-3bcb-4f14-a873-23c413554cc3.text: The gnome seems a little drunk.

bb4b8440-e8e7-405f-b34d-53d8b93e9c42.title: Gnome
bb4b8440-e8e7-405f-b34d-53d8b93e9c42.text: I don't think I can take much more!

acaeb34a-a789-4f8e-9e96-99fa51d3a5e7.title: Gnome
acaeb34a-a789-4f8e-9e96-99fa51d3a5e7.text: Can't stop sorry! Busy, busy, busy!

fb8de5c3-81b1-4549-8ce8-610494665086.text: The gnome is too busy to talk.

0f8e4edc-0fb6-4fe8-b687-2a7529b372d1.title: Gnome
0f8e4edc-0fb6-4fe8-b687-2a7529b372d1.text: It's just the wife, she won't stop moaning!

8b111e7c-52ae-4e6d-bbd0-a9f3cca9615c.title: <player>
8b111e7c-52ae-4e6d-bbd0-a9f3cca9615c.text: Maybe you should give her less to moan about.
